<p><a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Computer-mediated_communication&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
