<p>Forman, E.A. (2000). Knowledge building in discourse communities. Human Development, 43(6), 364-368.</p>
<p>Gabriel, M.A. (2004). Learning together: Exploring group interactions online. Journal of Distance Education, 19(1), 54-72.</p>
